# Operating preferences

> What this orchestrator has learned about how the CTO wants to
> work. Each entry is a recurring decision the orchestrator no
> longer asks about. Read by skills before they hit a known fork;
> updated by `/preferences` or by direct edit.
>
> **Discipline doc:** `.claude/preferences.md` (synced from kit).
> **Owning skill:** `/preferences`.

The format below is regenerated and sorted alphabetically by ID
when `/preferences` writes. Hand edits are preserved as long as
the per-entry shape is followed.

